DocAttribute.Name: OperatesOn
DocAttribute.Documentation: Set of Relationships to objects that are operated on by the process.

DocAttribute.Name: IsSuccessorFrom
DocAttribute.Documentation: Relative placement in time, refers to the previous processes for which this process is successor.

DocAttribute.Name: IsPredecessorTo
DocAttribute.Documentation: Relative placement in time, refers to the subsequent processes for which this process is predecessor.
